#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.floor.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.floor"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:1 of
msgid "Return the floor of the input, element-wise."
msgstr "按元素返回输入的下限。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:3 of
msgid ""
"The floor of the scalar `x` is the largest integer `i`, such that `i <= "
"x`.  It is often denoted as :math:`\\lfloor x \\rfloor`."
msgstr ""
"标量 `x` 的下限是最大的整数 `i`，使得 `i <= x`。通常表示为 :math:`\\"
"lfloor x \\rfloor`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:6 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:8 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有与输入广播兼容的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:13 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:18 of
msgid "**y** -- The floor of each element in `x`."
msgstr "**y** -- `x` 中每个元素的下限。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ceil`, :py:obj:`trunc`, :py:obj:`rint`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floor.floor:25 of
msgid ""
"Some spreadsheet programs calculate the \"floor-towards-zero\", in other "
"words ``floor(-2.5) == -2``.  NumPy instead uses the definition of "
"`floor` where `floor(-2.5) == -3`."
msgstr ""
"一些电子表格程序计算的是“向零取整”的下限，换句话说 ``floor(-2.5) == -2`"
"`。而 NumPy 使用的是 `floor` 的定义，即 `floor(-2.5) == -3`。"

